{"tid":2032082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你知道“香港共和国”在国语里怎么说吗？","createTime":"2020-05-23T23:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T00:57:57.000Z","uid":334191,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2be42272f2152ccfcc724668924fb88625077bbc","tid":2032082,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T23:37:19.000Z","msg":"这里说的国语，是满洲语&mdash;&mdash;大清国语。<br />\n隆重推出本人亲自编写的满洲语对话教程。<br />\n第一课&mdash;&mdash;自我介绍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FO7AgmK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFO7AgmK.png&h=9632fafa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86650e9814ab1f4e4d10c3a7b3089840b942c307","tid":2032082,"uid":303977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T23:38:36.000Z","msg":"皇道樂土"},{"pid":"21e855b2aa347c2e8ee835a421ae2dabf12307a0","tid":2032082,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2be42272f2152ccfcc724668924fb88625077bbc","tid":2032082,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T23:37:19.000Z","msg":"这里说的国语，是满洲语&mdash;&mdash;大清国语。<br />\n隆重推出本人亲自编写的满洲语对话教程。<br />\n第一课&mdash;&mdash;自我介绍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FO7AgmK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFO7AgmK.png&h=9632fafa&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T23:43:01.000Z","msg":"你點識的？"},{"pid":"d61941740cf57589fd24c69cef55ff5efa56fcd5","tid":2032082,"uid":334191,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"21e855b2aa347c2e8ee835a421ae2dabf12307a0","tid":2032082,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2be42272f2152ccfcc724668924fb88625077bbc","tid":2032082,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T23:37:19.000Z","msg":"这里说的国语，是满洲语&mdash;&mdash;大清国语。<br />\n隆重推出本人亲自编写的满洲语对话教程。<br />\n第一课&mdash;&mdash;自我介绍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FO7AgmK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFO7AgmK.png&h=9632fafa&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T23:43:01.000Z","msg":"你點識的？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T23:52:53.000Z","msg":"学的。<br />\n<br />\n香港共和国：Hong Kong Republik。其实&ldquo;共和&rdquo;一词已经被翻译为&quot;gunghe gurun&quot;。但这种翻译是从中文借入的二手货，&ldquo;共和&rdquo;本是西方传来的政治概念，直接从英文借入更符合满洲语自身的造词传统。<br />\n<br />\n同样的道理，这个教程里拒绝把&ldquo;中国&rdquo;称为Dulimbai Gurun （中央之国），因为在《满文老档》中，本来就有Nikan Gurun（尼堪国）这个词称呼中国，完全没有必要借入中国人表达自我中心主义的词。"},{"pid":"1d2ba8875c33ea2da8d65d9edd455f0638533565","tid":2032082,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d61941740cf57589fd24c69cef55ff5efa56fcd5","tid":2032082,"uid":334191,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"21e855b2aa347c2e8ee835a421ae2dabf12307a0","tid":2032082,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2be42272f2152ccfcc724668924fb88625077bbc","tid":2032082,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T23:37:19.000Z","msg":"这里说的国语，是满洲语&mdash;&mdash;大清国语。<br />\n隆重推出本人亲自编写的满洲语对话教程。<br />\n第一课&mdash;&mdash;自我介绍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FO7AgmK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFO7AgmK.png&h=9632fafa&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T23:43:01.000Z","msg":"你點識的？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T23:52:53.000Z","msg":"学的。<br />\n<br />\n香港共和国：Hong Kong Republik。其实&ldquo;共和&rdquo;一词已经被翻译为&quot;gunghe gurun&quot;。但这种翻译是从中文借入的二手货，&ldquo;共和&rdquo;本是西方传来的政治概念，直接从英文借入更符合满洲语自身的造词传统。<br />\n<br />\n同样的道理，这个教程里拒绝把&ldquo;中国&rdquo;称为Dulimbai Gurun （中央之国），因为在《满文老档》中，本来就有Nikan Gurun（尼堪国）这个词称呼中国，完全没有必要借入中国人表达自我中心主义的词。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T00:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d77b9b56d8131f623c65c97c079b617f976eb0","tid":2032082,"uid":100844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T00:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e46c1abb639a05492aeeef1b517700d62c68af","tid":2032082,"uid":338262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T00:57:57.000Z","msg":"點解打殘體"}]}